0.1.name: wordpress/oqey-headers
0.1.description:
oQey Headers plugin is a Wordpress Plugin that allows to add and manage images for blog header easily.

NEW: Add image description, you can add some text to your images. - suport for flash header.

For instruction on how to insert the plugin into wp template, please visit http://www.oqeysites.com
